              <span class="cited">3.8:1</span>, representing <span class="cited">$427,000</span> in measurable social value.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="mockup-section">
            <h4>Key Outcomes</h4>
            <ul class="mockup-list">
              <li><span class="cited">89%</span> of mentees reported increased confidence</li>
              <li><span class="cited">67%</span> achieved employment or education goals</li>
              <li><span class="cited">92%</span> volunteer retention rate</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="mockup-badge">
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71"/>
            </svg>
            Every highlighted claim is clickable and traced to source data
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA SECTION -->
  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="cta-background"></div>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-content">
        <span class="cta-label">GET STARTED</span>
        <h2>Create Your First Report</h2>
        <p>Stop spending weeks on impact reports. Start generating board-ready presentations in minutes.</p>
        <div class="cta-buttons">
          <a href="/en/cockpit/demo/reports" class="btn btn-primary">Generate Report Now</a>
